\"score\": 0.9776132267755008, \"rank\": 0.02229675142999901, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson, who grew up in the state's surfing heartland of Margaret River, won asilver medal, losing out to Tahitian hero Kauli Vaast in the gold medal match on Tuesday morning.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 676, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.8222049378152352, \"rank\": 0.21270803987688966, \"text\": \"Tahitian\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 696, \"end\": 701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Students at Margaret River High School's surfing academy gathered in the early hours of the morning, and during class, to cheer Robinson on.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surf student Ruby Berry not only counts Robinson as an inspiration, but also a former neighbour.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\", \"score\": 0.9999997541840759, \"rank\": 1.280084460313154e-07, \"text\": \"Ruby\", \"types\": [\"Q7946\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so stoked for him - everyone in the house was cheering,\\\" Ruby said.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\", \"score\": 0.9999997541840759, \"rank\": 1.280084460313154e-07, \"text\": \"Ruby\", \"types\": [\"Q7946\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruby\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember seeing him when I was little and now to see him at that level is so inspiring.\\\"\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jack Robinson in Tahiti, representing Australia in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.999059089488362, \"rank\": 0.0006410986056806744, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 1162, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999973942515069, \"rank\": 2.501271162917102e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 1195, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999987242203086, \"rank\": 1.273682498110125e-06, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied: Jojo Alpers from Surfing Australia)  Olive Hardy said Robinson was a supportive presence at the local surf breaks.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surfing_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Surfing Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surfing_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surfing_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1275, \"end\": 1280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Hardy\", \"score\": 0.9989521598298291, \"rank\": 0.0010489392909726503, \"text\": \"Hardy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Hardy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Hardy\"}, {\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is so nice to all the groms - you will see him anywhere and he will instantly be like 'that was a sick turn' if he sees you out in the surf,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jack Robinson walks away with his Margaret River Pro trophy in 2022.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1505, \"end\": 1509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.999059089488362, \"rank\": 0.0006410986056806744, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 1510, \"end\": 1518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_River_Pro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.323160302274231e-13, \"text\": \"Margaret River Pro\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_River_Pro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Margaret_River_Pro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(ABC South West: Georgia Hargreaves)  A plaque bearing Robinson's name is already fixed to the stairs of Margaret River's famed Surfers Point following his win at the 2022 World Surf League competition.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999998732555548, \"rank\": 1.26744584469701e-07, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_West_England\", \"score\": 0.9999870799822654, \"rank\": 1.2618155249470115e-05, \"text\": \"South West\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_West_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_West_England\"}, {\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow academy member Macklin Flynn hinted the local shire should go one up in the wake of Robinson's silver medal performance.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\", \"score\": 0.9999999385495376, \"rank\": 6.145037893347313e-08, \"text\": \"Flynn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Errol_Flynn\"}, {\"begin\": 1868, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think he should have a street named after him,\\\" Macklin said.\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A silver at the Olympics is so sick.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It inspires me to also achieve that result and maybe go one better.\\\"\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watching on from Taihiti, Robinson's mother Mersina said winning an Olympic medal was better than any world title.\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.642063503955534, \"rank\": 0.5539296930017099, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2126, \"end\": 2133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mersin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mersina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mersin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mersin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics is huge,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think, personally, it's bigger than than winning a world title - it's once every four years.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even a silver medal is amazing to get to this point is fantastic.\\\"\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The celebrations look set to continue for South West residents.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Busselton's Nina Kennedy is going for gold in the pole vault in the early hours of Thursday morning.\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2464, \"end\": 2473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busselton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.349417507749975e-16, \"text\": \"Busselton\",